CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 13, 1945, pg. 4, reads: "Photo Presented For Weil School - The Soho Community association, of which David B. Roberts is president, presented a large portrait of the late Judge Ralph Smith to the faculty and students of A. Leo Weil school on Monday, which was the birth-date of the late jurist.  John B. Thompson of the Soho Community association made the presentation to Principal George Culberson.  Judge Joseph A. Richardson is shown holding the picture. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: John B. Thompson, Judge Joseph A. Richardson, and George Culberson gathered around photograph of Judge Ralph H. Smith in A. Leo Weil School
